   Here is the list of winners announced
Monday night at the 41st Cannes Film Festival:
   _Golden Palm: ``Pelle the Conqueror'' by Danish director Bille
August, starring Max von Sydow and Pelle Hvenegaard.
   _Best Actress: Shared by Barbara Hershey of the United States,
Linda Mvusi of South Africa and Jodhi May of Britain for their
roles in ``A World Apart.''
