   _Technical Excellence: ``Bird'' soundtrack.
   _Golden Palm for Best Short Film: ``Ornament'' by Soviet
director Gary Bardine.
   _Best Animated Film: ``Tracks in the Sand'' by Hungarian
director Ferenc Cako.
   _Best Short Fiction Film: ``Sculpture Physique'' by French
directors Yann Piquer and Jean-Marie Maddedu.
